installationInstructions.title: Food was freezing in the fridge
installationInstructions.content: Spoke to a repair technician online described what was happening as food keep freezing in the fridge.He advised me to change the thermistor and if that didn't work the control board as those are the only 2 things that would cause food to freeze.Changed thermistor and fridge is running at proper temp very disappointed with whirlpool as fridge is only 2 years old and had issues already .Now that its repaired its Time for a COLD beer !!!
